query:
SELECT
  pb.id,
  b.link,
  b.title,
  b.thumbnail_url,
  b.published_at,
  b.author,
  coalesce(
    array_agg(ROW (t.id, t.title)) FILTER (
      WHERE
        t.id IS NOT NULL
    ),
    ARRAY[]::record[]
  ) AS "tags!: Vec<Tag>"
FROM
  profile_bookmarks AS pb
  INNER JOIN bookmarks AS b ON b.id = pb.bookmark_id
  LEFT JOIN profile_bookmark_tags AS pbt ON pbt.profile_bookmark_id = pb.id
  LEFT JOIN tags AS t ON pbt.tag_id = t.id
WHERE
  pb.id = $1
  AND pb.profile_id = $2
GROUP BY
  pb.id,
  b.link,
  b.title,
  b.thumbnail_url,
  b.published_at,
  b.author;
